---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy"
  description="BestKarma privacy information for website visitors and newsletter subscribers."
>
  <section class="bg-cream-dark/60 border-b border-border">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
      <p class="text-sage-dark text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Privacy</p>
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold text-bark">A short, plain-language privacy notice</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-stone">
        BestKarma keeps privacy expectations simple: we collect the minimum needed to run the site, deliver the newsletter, and understand what content is useful.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <div class="space-y-8">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border bg-white/70 p-8">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-semibold text-bark">Newsletter subscriptions</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-stone leading-relaxed">
          If you subscribe, your email address is sent to Beehiiv so BestKarma can deliver newsletter issues and onboarding emails. You can unsubscribe at any time from the footer of any email.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border bg-white/70 p-8">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-semibold text-bark">Site usage data</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-stone leading-relaxed">
          BestKarma may collect lightweight analytics about pages visited, referral sources, and newsletter conversions so the site can improve the reader experience.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border bg-white/70 p-8">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-semibold text-bark">No sale of personal information</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-stone leading-relaxed">
          BestKarma does not sell subscriber email addresses. Any third-party services used to operate the site should be limited to hosting, delivery, and analytics functions.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border bg-mist p-8">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-semibold text-bark">Questions</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-stone leading-relaxed">
          If the site adds more tracking, cookies, ads, or commerce in the future, this page should be updated before those changes go live.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
